in City THE Edo State Police Commissioner, DanMallam Muhammed, has confirmed the release of the wife of Nigeria Railway Corporation (NRC) Managing Director, Mrs. Francisca Okhiria, who was abducted by gunmen in Benin City about two weeks ago. The police commissioner also said that investigation has shown… October 10, 2019 In "News"